= SDL_AtomicTryLock =
Use this function to try to lock a spin lock by setting it to a non-zero value.


== Syntax ==
```c++
SDL_bool SDL_AtomicTryLock(SDL_SpinLock* lock)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''lock'''
|points to the lock
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns SDL_TRUE if the lock succeeded, SDL_FALSE if the lock is already held.

